%N A082042 a(n) = (n^2+1)*n!.
%C A082042 Main diagonal of A082037
%C A082042 a(n) = total number of runs when each permutation on [n+1] is split into maximal monotone runs. (A monotone run is a sequence of consecutive entries whose differences are all 1 or all -1. Example: 34-1-765-2 contributes 4 runs to a(6) as indicated.) - _David Callan_, Nov 16 2003
%C A082042 a(n) is also the number of distinct planar embeddings of the (n+1)-Sierpinski gasket graph. - _Eric W. Weisstein_, May 21 2024
